間上冇野可以留戀<br />\n(佢笑呀！！！佢對我笑呀！！)<br />\n<br />\n然後連尼住飲完枱上杯紫色嘢飲之後俾錢埋單走人<br />\n<br />\n連尼住返到屋企之後， 即刻同佢個網友傾計<br />\n「連連：望望！今日我見到個靚仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    望望：咁你有冇抄佢牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    連連：邊夠膽喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    望望：無鬼用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    連連：我都唔想㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    望望： 話時話我哋識咗幾個月都未出嚟一齊食過嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    連連：又係喎，3日後係聖誕節，嗰日出嚟一齊玩好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n    望望： 不如我哋叫多一兩個friend出嚟玩好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多啲人好玩啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    連連：好呀好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    望望：好啦，1234567890呢個我電話，3日後call我，瞓先 bye<br />\n    連連：好呀，bye，btw 凌晨玩你電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    望望：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n                                                                                        」<br />\n<br />\n待續。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b1ef23aab4027824b12b4900305138ab41be92d","tid":38748,"uid":37168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:12:55.000Z","msg":"樓主未作完譚仔變態故就想開新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be779e934aa8c0cf07eb5962b9d0aab98dabcc24","tid":38748,"uid":37168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:13:40.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6eb19dfac911da06827557e4354e258d9d