                                              」<br />\n然後連尼住就同網友傾計<br />\n「連連：望望，仲有兩日咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    望望：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 你尋晚係咪玩我電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    連連：無呀，我無呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    望望：咁係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 朋友嗰到你約成點， 我約咗        一個<br />\n    連連：唔知道呀唔係我吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係約咗一個<br />\n    望望：咁好啦到時見啦 瞓先 bye<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    連連：好啦 bye<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  btw 其實係我玩你電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今晚再玩過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    望望：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />                                    」<br />\n待續。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83705ff6643745f3db37cf13f317723737b68cc5","tid":38748,"uid":579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T08:05:24.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b397da2f251dc0ae310868b7c40d0f8da2d180c4","tid":38748,"uid":34500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T08:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6944a7a727ac5d90914d9cb69f3598fdbf4b9ea","tid":38748,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T08:09:51.000Z","msg":"留名睇<br />\n望遠 連尼住巴入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im